    A2 -- assembled --> K2["<b>each opponent draws 7 → ~14–28 life loss each (lethal-or-bust — never spin on one)</b><br/>⏱ table T9"]:::table
    A2 --> A3{"Peer into the Abyss aimed at one opponent<br/>with a draw-punisher out"}:::ask
